Comment: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows what it's like
Comment: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the bad man
Comment: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the sad man
Comment: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind blue eyes
Comment: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows what it's like
Comment: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To be hated
Comment: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To be fated
Comment: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To telling only lies
Comment: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But my dreams
Comment: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't as empty
Comment: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As my conscience seems to be
