Comment: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,BAKE PIES DURING WARS. A TRUE RUSSIAN WIFE.
Comment: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:32.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,..ho..

Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As a soldier, I too have killed people,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,just like you, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have suffered enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:53.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So I will forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:58.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if no one else will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:06.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:42.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds are now healed. I am practicing the trumpet every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:11.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A large contingent of Roman forces has appeared on the border between Seize and Nomansland?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:35.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:41.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have captured the Roman soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:43.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:45.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. She is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:46.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:52.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our battalion will now join forces with the First and Third Divisions in transit to the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:53.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:54.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:56.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you move, I will shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:58.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:01.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:05.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Command your troops to leave the fortress immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:08.14,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}Echo Through the Blue Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:10.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:12.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Treason!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:16.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those girls in the fortress have taken our commanding officer hostage and barricaded themselves in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:17.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, it didn't hit any of her major organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:26.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her condition should stay stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:28.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sister Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:32.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:36.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl was going to be a sacrifice to start the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't be worth much dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:39.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This last month,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:48.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,we've been following Roman forces as they mobilized for an attack from a rear front.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:53.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably another bargaining chip in the peace conferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:55.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They took us lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:02:00.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Archduke has cold feet - he specifically ordered us not to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:05.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need one little push so they attack us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:11.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A little push, like a prisoner of war, executed by firing squad, crying and screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:12.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:13.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace is just a worthless play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:17.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rome must be thrown into ruin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:20.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so, Noël Kannagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:24.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, our hero, the Witch of Helvetia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I wouldn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:31.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Noël was just used by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:33.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Noël...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:37.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really were involved with the Invisible Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Invisible Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:45.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest genius the Academy has known in over a hundred years - the Invisible Death -
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:48.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who restored that ancient biological weapons plant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,is the girl sitting before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:55.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your talent is wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to work under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock this man in the distillery downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:14.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our compatriots are already in transit for battle with the Roman army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:17.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One small tap and the scenario will play itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:23.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's back to the battlefield for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:26.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when you think it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got some bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel has been locked in the distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:34.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:45.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and eat these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:48.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sweets I stocked up on in Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:49.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave when it really gets bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all completely messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:03.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of the Fire protect the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're throwing the town into the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:08.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were hiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:14.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the legend of the Maidens of the Fire from Miss A'ishah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:21.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that a completely different legend was passed down in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:27.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of the Fire protect life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:51.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the shift change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:55.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need to. I can't leave you to do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:59.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can shoot a gun at someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:06.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I think that it's the right thing to do, I might.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:11.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the Maidens of the Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:14.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the Maidens of the Fire before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:20.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What, do you actually believe that story? That fairy tale that Roman made up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:23.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Something about it clicks with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:26.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of the Fire protect life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it must have been that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:35.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:46.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:47.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:50.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:06:00.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how good her ears are, she can't possibly hear it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A cease-fire signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:08.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:10.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:13.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:20.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She might have just heard things. And even if it were, we don't know if the treaty has been signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we must inform Colonel Hopkins that-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:28.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency! When I went to bring him food, the Colonel wasn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence attack in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:36.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the Colonel will actually listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in not trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:52.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:03.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When he saw the people dead from the Death I resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:10.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Until there's no one left to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:17.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I helped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:23.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think so, then save more lives than you took.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:25.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:31.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:35.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ceasefire? Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can trust her ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:39.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We'll vouch for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:44.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's easily amused, she forgets everything, she's just like a little kid, and she's not sexy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest this old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:50.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want war that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:55.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,War advances civilization and science.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:58.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to restore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Man's former glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:07.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Roman army is set to attack tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:12.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's no way to stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:33.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy! We're up against the Demon of Binnenland!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to deliver it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone gave me this sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:42.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are being selfish. You do not do things because you decide them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:50.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone once said that the world was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:54.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I love this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:58.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this town. I love everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:03.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:14.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah is begging you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:16.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:44.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Same...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:50.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have suffered enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:29.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, A'ishah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go, there's no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:41.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,have no objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:03.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been objecting for us this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:08.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:12.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,want someone my age...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:17.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,going through torture either! But Rio isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:23.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And Noël and Kanata are lax...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:28.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So I had to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:32.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm such a bad commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:34.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:41.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:44.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My myriad gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:48.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,let your blessings be upon the Maidens of the Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:59.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Primary converter reactor output rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:04.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,FAP, FAC, DMR, and ECP all green.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:07.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Superconducting circuits, function stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:10.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire control system also good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:14.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Primary and secondary armaments are operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:16.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Release all joint locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:23.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Weight-reduction system operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:26.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Factor of minus... about five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:29.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepared to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:32.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We do it just like we practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, my little ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Main armament, standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:39.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Load shell! AP round!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Loading AP round!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:51.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Target locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:53.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:54.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:55.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They're in that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:59.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To restore the pinnacle of ancient technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:04.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal all units! All possible measures to prevent escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had enough of your war!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:14.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to get them, get us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:15.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Demon of Binnenland.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:36.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go around! Join with the forces at our rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:45.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of the Fire protect life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:50.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is in your hands, Miss Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:15:00.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,long before the world turned out this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:06.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An angel that God sent to deliver divine retribution upon the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:11.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,was injured, and set her wings down to rest in a town at the Western end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:22.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the maidens that lived in the fortress that saved her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:26.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the one sent to bring them ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:32.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the maidens took pity upon the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,With the aid of a giant spider,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,they sheltered the angel in the valley below.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:44.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To stifle the blood springing from her, the maidens,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:47.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,each in turn, held the head of the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:54.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And in thanks, the angel granted them a golden horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:16:01.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But eventually, the people of the town learned of the angel's presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}and set fire to the bottom of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:08.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The maidens were lost to the fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the angel's head taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:13.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and their suffering ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:22.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, the host of angels appeared, filling the sky above the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:26.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, a miracle happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:30.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the sky echoed on high,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:32.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and the angels departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:41.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,With her last breath, the last maiden of the fortress sounded the golden horn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:45.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and saved the lives of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:01.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you remember that young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you gave the caramel to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:07.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to get thrown into this too, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:09.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All units, prepare to charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:13.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't do anything about that. We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:18.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:29.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an allied vehicle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:40.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Under command of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon 1121!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:17:59.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A cease-fire signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's a Roman signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major General!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't pull back now! Main armament, standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:18.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. They're not stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:19.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That young lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:18.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! You will fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Both sides, lay down your arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:38.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am second in line to the throne of Helvetia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:43.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,daughter of the royal family of Helvetia, fiancée to the Emperor of the Holy Roman Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:46.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio Kazumiya Arkadia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am here in the name of my father, the Archduke of Helvetia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and the name of the Roman Emperor, to announce:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:57.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have peace! There will be no more fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Both sides will disband immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an imperial command!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:10.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who do not comply will be punished by the First Royal Guard of Helvetia under both names!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:19.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:56.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:21:59.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:30.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure feels like spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.27,0:22:36.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, Noël, what did A'ishah say in her letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:42.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Translate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:46.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am well. I am practicing the trumpet every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:48.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.12,0:22:52.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We even get letters from Rome,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:55.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but we still don't get any from the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:57.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's just really busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:22:59.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio is a princess, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.18,0:23:05.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I mean, she was surrounded by the Royal Guard back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:07.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't even talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:10.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Klaus's bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:19.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:22.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, new recruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:23.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to beat-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.17,0:23:48.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, I have been assigned to Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:50.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Lieutenant Rio Kazumiya Arkadia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:54.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Filicia Heidemann, requesting permission to perform duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.88,0:23:56.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:23:59.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no ranks here, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:06.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Well, the Roman Emperor is actually a pretty reasonable guy and, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:12.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,he told me he would grant me one wish as thanks for ending the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:14.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.66,0:24:19.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:21.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.16,0:24:23.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.25,0:24:26.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Welcome home, Rio.
